            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EPrayer%20is%20our%20occupation.%20It%20is%20not%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20halfhearted%2C%20wishful%20endeavor%2C%20but%20rather%20it%20should%20be%20wholehearted%2C%20intense%2C%20fervent%2C%20and%20devoted.%20What%20a%20privilege%20it%20is%20for%20us%20to%20engage%20in%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20will%20change%20everything!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EEpaphras%20was%20a%20mighty%20prayer%20warrior%20who%20wrestled%20in%20prayer%20for%20the%20Colossians%20(Colossians%204%3A12%20NIV).%20The%20word%20wrestle%20means%20%22to%20agonize%2C%22%20or%20%22to%20wrestle%20as%20in%20a%20wrestling%20match.%22%20In%20Epaphras's%20day%2C%20wrestling%20was%20the%20most%20intense%20athletic%20match%20in%20the%20Olympics%2C%20and%20for%20Paul%20to%20describe%20Epaphras's%20prayer%20as%20%22wrestling%22%20shows%20the%20intensity%20with%20which%20this%20brother%20labored%20in%20prayer.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EEpaphras's%20fervent%20prayer%20was%20that%20the%20Colossians%20might%20be%20%22strong%20and%20perfect%2C%20fully%20confident%20of%20the%20whole%20will%20of%20God%22%20(v.%2012).%20Satan%20is%20continually%20opposing%20the%20will%20of%20God%20in%20our%20lives%2C%20and%20only%20through%20wrestling%2C%20agonizing%20prayer%20can%20the%20will%20of%20God%20be%20accomplished.%20Epaphras%20was%20willing%20to%20agonize%20over%20the%20Colossian%20church.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGod%20told%20the%20prophet%20Jeremiah%2C%20%22Pray%20no%20more%20for%20these%20people%2C%20Jeremiah.%20Do%20not%20weep%20or%20pray%20for%20them%2C%20for%20I%20will%20not%20listen%20to%20them%20when%20they%20cry%20out%20to%20me%20in%20distress%22%20(Jeremiah%2011%3A14).%20We%20may%20wrestle%20in%20prayer%20on%20behalf%20of%20others%2C%20but%20they%20bear%20the%20responsibility%20of%20responding%20to%20God's%20overtures.%20What%20a%20tragedy%20it%20is%20when%20people%20resist%20God%20so%20much%20that%20He%20will%20no%20longer%20hear%20prayer%20on%20their%20behalf!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELet%20us%20wrestle%2C%20watch%2C%20and%20agonize%20in%20prayer%20daily.%20Our%20families%20and%20friends%20are%20depending%20upon%20us.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
