            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2010%3A1-11%3A23%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EIdolatry%20Brings%20Destruction%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EHear%20the%20word%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20speaks%20to%20you%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BIsrael!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BDo%20not%20act%20like%20the%20other%20nations%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20try%20to%20read%20their%20future%20in%20the%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EDo%20not%20be%20afraid%20of%20their%20predictions%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eeven%20though%20other%20nations%20are%20terrified%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ETheir%20ways%20are%20futile%20and%20foolish.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20cut%20down%20a%20tree%2C%20and%20a%20craftsman%20carves%20an%20idol.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20decorate%20it%20with%20gold%20and%20silver%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20then%20fasten%20it%20securely%20with%20hammer%20and%20nails%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20it%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20fall%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3ETheir%20gods%20are%20like%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehelpless%20scarecrows%20in%20a%20cucumber%20field!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20cannot%20speak%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20they%20need%20to%20be%20carried%20because%20they%20cannot%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EDo%20not%20be%20afraid%20of%20such%20gods%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20they%20can%20neither%20harm%20you%20nor%20do%20you%20any%20good.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20there%20is%20no%20one%20like%20you!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EFor%20you%20are%20great%2C%20and%20your%20name%20is%20full%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWho%20would%20not%20fear%20you%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BKing%20of%20nations%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThat%20title%20belongs%20to%20you%20alone!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EAmong%20all%20the%20wise%20people%20of%20the%20earth%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20in%20all%20the%20kingdoms%20of%20the%20world%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethere%20is%20no%20one%20like%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EPeople%20who%20worship%20idols%20are%20stupid%20and%20foolish.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20things%20they%20worship%20are%20made%20of%20wood!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20bring%20beaten%20sheets%20of%20silver%20from%20Tarshish%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20gold%20from%20Uphaz%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Eand%20they%20give%20these%20materials%20to%20skillful%20craftsmen%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20make%20their%20idols.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThen%20they%20dress%20these%20gods%20in%20royal%20blue%20and%20purple%20robes%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Emade%20by%20expert%20tailors.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_10%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20the%20only%20true%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHe%20is%20the%20living%20God%20and%20the%20everlasting%20King!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20whole%20earth%20trembles%20at%20his%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20nations%20cannot%20stand%20up%20to%20his%20wrath.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_10_11%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ESay%20this%20to%20those%20who%20worship%20other%20gods%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BYour%20so-called%20gods%2C%20who%20did%20not%20make%20the%20heavens%20and%20earth%2C%20will%20vanish%20from%20the%20earth%20and%20fro